areer/person/\"><span class=\"txt\">人を知る</span></a></li>\n          <li class=\"g-nav__li\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/recruit/\"><span class=\"txt\">採用情報</span></a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n      <p class=\"g-nav__btn g-nav__link\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-new\">新卒採用はこちら</a></p>\n      <p class=\"g-nav__btn g-nav__entry\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/application/\">エントリー</a></p>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- header △-->\n\n<main class=\"ps-r \">\n  <section class=\"page__mv ps-r\">\n    <figure class=\"pmv__img\">\n          <img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/person/person_mv.jpg\" alt=\"メインビジュアル\">\n        </figure>\n    <h2 class=\"pmv__ttl\">\n              <span class=\"font-en\">person</span>\n            <span class=\"font-min\">人を知る</span>\n    </h2>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ▽content | Sub-contents -->\n\n    \n<section class=\"p-contents section ps-r\">\n      <div class=\"p-cont--top\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n          <h2 class=\"p-ct__ttl p-section__ttl mb-80\"><span class=\"font-en font-en color-ma\">EMPLOYEE INTERVIEW</span><span class=\"font-min\">社員インタビュー</span></h2>\n          <p class=\"p-ct__lead fs-20 al-center mb-30 lh-2\">\n            若⼿からベテランまで、奥井組で働く現役社員に<br class=\"spnone\">\n            ⼊社のきっかけから⽇々の仕事内容ややりがい、そして未来への展望などについて聞きました。\n          </p>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <article class=\"pc__atc atc01\">\n        <div class=\"inner__large ps-r\">\n          <div class=\"pc__atc--flex flex jc-between\">\n            <div class=\"pca__txtwarp\">\n              <div class=\"pca__txtwrap--inner\">\n                <h3 class=\"pca__copy fs-36 font-min mb-20\">\n                  完全未経験から主任に。<br>\n                  働きやすさの秘密は上司・先輩の<br class=\"spnone\">「人の良さ」。\n                </h3>\n                <div class=\"pca__infowrap\">\n                  <p class=\"pca__name mb-60\">\n                    <span class=\"info fs-18\">物流事業部 2020年6月21日入職</span>\n                    <span class=\"name fs-24\">佐藤 竜二<span class=\"fs-18\">（中途採用）</span></span>\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"pca__btn font-en\"><a class=\"link__btn\" href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice01/\">VIEW\n                      MORE<i class=\"arw fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></a></p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"pca__imgwrap\">\n              <figure class=\"pca__img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/person/a-atc_staff01.png\" alt=\"社員\"></figure>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"pc__atc atc02 reverse\">\n        <div class=\"inner__large ps-r\">\n          <div class=\"pc__atc--flex flex jc-between\">\n            <div class=\"pca__imgwrap\">\n              <figure class=\"pca__img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/person/a-atc_staff02.png\" alt=\"社員\"></figure>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"pca__txtwarp\">\n              <div class=\"pca__txtwrap--inner\">\n                <h3 class=\"pca__copy fs-36 font-min mb-20\">\n                  やる気があれば、どんな人でも輝ける。<br>\n                  夢のある大きな仕事ができるのは、<br class=\"spnone\">\n                  老舗の奥井組だからこそ。\n                </h3>\n                <div class=\"pca__infowrap\">\n                  <p class=\"pca__name mb-60\">\n                    <span class=\"info fs-18\">運輸事業部 2020年6月21日入職</span>\n                    <span class=\"name fs-24\">岡本 順一<span class=\"fs-18\">（中途採用）</span></span>\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"pca__btn font-en\"><a class=\"link__btn\" href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice02/\">VIEW\n                      MORE<i class=\"arw fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></a></p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"pc__atc atc03\">\n        <div class=\"inner__large ps-r\">\n          <div class=\"pc__atc--flex flex jc-between\">\n            <div class=\"pca__txtwarp\">\n              <div class=\"pca__txtwrap--inner\">\n                <h3 class=\"pca__copy fs-36 font-min mb-20\">\n                  仲が良いからこそ仕事がスムーズに進む。<br>資格取得でやりがいも十分。\n                </h3>\n                <div class=\"pca__infowrap\">\n                  <p class=\"pca__name mb-60\">\n                    <span class=\"info fs-18\">プラント機工事業部 2017年入社</span>\n                    <span class=\"name fs-24\">東 直斗<span class=\"fs-18\">（新卒採用）</span></span>\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"pca__btn font-en\"><a class=\"link__btn\" href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice03/\">VIEW\n                      MORE<i class=\"arw fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></a></p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"pca__imgwrap\">\n              <figure class=\"pca__img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/person/a-atc_staff03.jpg\" alt=\"社員\"></figure>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"pc__atc atc04 reverse\">\n        <div class=\"inner__large ps-r\">\n          <div class=\"pc__atc--flex flex jc-between\">\n            <div class=\"pca__imgwrap\">\n              <figure class=\"pca__img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/person/a-atc_staff04.jpg\" alt=\"社員\"></figure>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"pca__txtwarp\">\n              <div class=\"pca__txtwrap--inner\">\n                <h3 class=\"pca__copy fs-36 font-min mb-20\">\n                  上司・先輩に支えられて日々成⻑。<br>奥井組を選んで本当に良かった。\n                </h3>\n                <div class=\"pca__infowrap\">\n                  <p class=\"pca__name mb-60\">\n                    <span class=\"info fs-18\">現 建設事業部 土木施工部 2019年入社</span>\n                    <span class=\"name fs-24\">戸ヶ崎 達也<span class=\"fs-18\">（新卒採用）</span></span>\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"pca__btn font-en\"><a class=\"link__btn\" href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice04/\">VIEW\n                      MORE<i class=\"arw fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></a></p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <div class=\"p-other \">\n        <div class=\"inner__large\">\n          <h3 class=\"p-pther__ttl fs-40 bold al-center mb-50\"><span>＼</span>その他のインタビュー動画はこちら<span>／</span></h3>\n          <div class=\"p-othe__flex flex jc-between\">\n            <div class=\"p-other__item\">\n              <div class=\"ytwrap mb-20\">\n                <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JkXbBAE7CJY?si=D98HoH9gZzYrDSpu\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"p-other__info fs-22 al-center\">プラント機工事業部　2022年入社</p>\n              <h4 class=\"p-othe__name fs-36 al-center\">室加 簾<span class=\"fs-26\">（新卒採用）</span></h4>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-other__item\">\n              <div class=\"ytwrap mb-20\">\n                <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QPL18DNX1Qc?si=qU7WukOknIZl684Y\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"p-other__info fs-22 al-center\">現 建設事業部 建築施工部　2022年入社</p>\n              <h4 class=\"p-othe__name fs-36 al-center\">醍醐 秀明<span class=\"fs-26\">（中途採用）</span></h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </section>\n\n  <!-- ▲content | Sub-contents -->\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"ps-r scrollAnime\">\n  <p class=\"ft__btn ps-a font-min\">\n    <a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/application/\">\n      <span class=\"txt\">募集要項へ</span>\n      <img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/cmn/btn_arw_wh.png\" alt=\"矢印\">\n    </a>\n  </p>\n  <div class=\"inner ps-r\">\n    <div class=\"ft__navwrap\">\n      <ul class=\"ft__nav ft__nav01 flex jc-between\">\n        <li class=\"ft-nav__li sub-trigger\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/about/\"><span class=\"txt\">奥井組を知る</span></a>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"ft-nav__li\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/business/\"><span class=\"txt\">事業を知る</span></a></li>\n        <li class=\"ft-nav__li sub-trigger phase-2\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/\"><span class=\"txt\">人を知る</span></a>\n          <ul class=\"ft__subnav\">\n            <li class=\"ft__subnav--li\"><span class=\"txt\">社員インタビュー</span></li>\n            <li class=\"ft__subnav--li sub\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice01/\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/cmn/ft_subnav_ico.png\" alt=\"アイコン\">社員①物流事業部</a></li>\n            <li class=\"ft__subnav--li sub\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice02/\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/cmn/ft_subnav_ico.png\" alt=\"アイコン\">社員②運輸事業部</a></li>\n            <li class=\"ft__subnav--li sub\"><a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice03/\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/cmn/ft_subnav_ico.png\" alt=\"アイコン\">社員③プラント機工事業部</a></li>\n            <li class=\"ft__subnav--li sub\"><a 